{"tid":1564371,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"簡單講, 《願榮光歸香港》, 我想將 \"抹\" 改做 \"撤\"","createTime":"2019-09-12T17:36:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-12T18:02:10.000Z","uid":269005,"like":3,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"4f4f215254c388a73f1e832ac419edad0eba5dec","tid":1564371,"uid":269005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T17:36:10.000Z","msg":"如題. 冇興趣可以唔睇下面.<br />\n我認衰仔, 我後知後覺, 因為唔係成日上連登.<br />\n我知, MV 都出埋, 改乜鬼.<br />\n但有一個字, 我真係覺得可以考慮.<br />\n就係, 將 &quot;抹不走&quot; 改為 &quot;撤不走&quot;<br />\n比較啱音順口, 唱得響. 第一音重音你嗌到幾大聲都得.<br />\n冇錯, 恐懼本身可以用抹走或者掃走, 完全正確. <br />\n假如將 &quot;何以這恐懼抹不走&quot; 改為 &quot;何以這恐懼<span style=\"color: red;\">撤</span>不走&quot;,<br />\n可以表示為 就算惡法撤回, 恐懼仍然存在, 有另一層(抽水)嘅意思.<br />\n更重要嘅考慮係, 呢首歌留返個位放個 &quot;撤&quot; 字落去, 應該冇人反對.<br />\n唔改唔緊要, 而家個版本已經好好. 如果原著仍有改動空間, 請考慮一下.<br />\n香港人加油!<br />\n好人一生平安!"},{"pid":"88ccd3b0b335f6135552ca45c054c30bd617b47a","tid":1564371,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T17:36:28.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPJ3iwW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaPJ3iwW.png&h=bd74ec1d&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"fbb2197f91e2760a17ced13b9c03b3003c53d736","tid":1564371,"uid":152108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T17:38:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8aef6bc739668b0a5a24cde5e5f5cf6e00aa3ba1","tid":1564371,"uid":169,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T17:39:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"539cffd2814646fd9cc2fd371d59a041487bbaf1","tid":1564371,"uid":55955,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T17:41:40.000Z","msg":"意思唔係好啱喎"},{"pid":"75e891d3212dc8f59b9e28c8af5cde84bfd828de","tid":1564371,"uid":41963,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8aef6bc739668b0a5a24cde5e5f5cf6e00aa3ba1","tid":1564371,"uid":169,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T17:39:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T17:41:46.000Z","msg":"國歌又好<br />\n軍歌又好<br />\n咁多不確定句同問句點凝聚戰意<br />\n要首歌流傳後世就真係要改<br />\nfor今次的話就冇乜所謂"},{"pid":"8c2072a5e67952472438c6299436f8aa4cfec795","tid":1564371,"uid":258696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T17:42:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />個個都唔知有咩行動<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />對唔對得住烈士同被捕手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>星期五 <span style=\"color: red;\">獅子山之路</span> 7:30 樂富 <br />\n</strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9KQxrNJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9KQxrNJ.png&h=c869dffa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>星期六 <span style=\"color: red;\">天水圍親子遊行</span> 2:30 天秀公園</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/O0LtKzJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/th